## Output

Every field in the final schema carries:

```json
{
  "testator": {
    "value":  "John Smith",
    "status": "found",
    "citation": {
      "segment_id": "article_1",
      "text": "I, John Smith, being of sound and disposing mind..."
    }
  },
  "first_death": {
    "value":  null,
    "status": "absent",
    "reason": "no survivorship clause present in assigned articles",
    "citation": null
  },
  "no_contest_clause": {
    "value":  null,
    "status": "requires_review",
    "reason": "max correction attempts reached",
    "citation": null
  }
}
```

